You can download the zip-packed code directly from the web page or using git
by executing the statement in the directory where you want to store the code:
    git clone https://github.com/bulanek/alive
The single binary file for Windows users (Linux user with Wine software) is stored in folder "bin".
The code is stored in src directory.
All the documentation about the program, running and developement, is in  html file
index.html in doc/html directory  or pdf file in doc/latex/refman.pdf.

